                        <interp inst="t18470920-2265-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>.</hi> Aged 27.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">ALLEN</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18470920-2265-verdict-3" type="verdictDescription">
